data.description: PARADISE AT CEDAR CREEK LAKE! Gorgeous wooded lake lot in the NEW gated community, Edgewater at Cedar Creek Lake!! You can build your dream home on 1.61 acres of dock-able lakefront property with NO time limit to build! Very private and secluded with it being the last lot on the cul-de-sac. Edgewater is a 250 acre gated development with approx. 145 home sites that will be built in the community. Underground utilities in place, nice streets, fire hydrants, lakefront pavilion with boat docks and park for residence. Lots of plans for this community! Great fishing at Cedar Creek Lake!
